                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "Two Actions"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per hour",
                    "effect": "You throw wide your arms, putting the golden gloves on full display and causing a blazing halo to form above your head. All enemies within a 40-feet emanation must make a DC 41 Fortitude save or be dazzled for 1 minute (or blinded for 1 minute on critical failure). Unholy creatures take a \u20132 item penalty to their roll. The halo then melts into your body and attempts to counteract any one affliction you are currently suffering of your choice with a counteract rank of 9 and a counteract modifier of +31.",
